data.description: $10,000 Seller Credit Towards Interest Rate Buy Down or Closing Costs AND... NO HOA DUES UNTIL 2025!!!  Discover the Crown Jewel of Allenmore Ridge! Top Floor End Unit, Nestled atop the 18th tee box in a secured community w/ elevator & stair access- picturesque 270° views of Allenmore Golf Course & Mount Rainier are the ultimate backdrop! Kitchen showcases new appliances, soft-close cabinetry, wine cooler & quartz countertops. Every detail meticulously designed, from remodeled bathrooms w/ state-of-the-art ventilation & Bluetooth audio, to barn door closets. Luxury extends to the new hardwood flooring, top-of-the-line lighting & tracking fixtures. Natural light abounds in the skylight dining room. Loft area & Mini-split A/C.
